Australia Defeats Sri Lanka to Clinch One-Day Cricket Series

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-08-20T15:14:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-20/australia-defeats-sri-lanka-to-clinch-one-day-cricket-series.html
Australia  defeated  Sri Lanka  by five
wickets in their fourth one-day cricket match to clinch victory
in the series.  The win in  Colombo , Sri Lanka, gives Australia an
unbeatable 3-1 lead in the five-game series, which concludes in
two days.  Brett Lee and Xavier Doherty took four wickets each as Sri
Lanka was dismissed for 132. Shaun Marsh then scored 70 and
 Michael Clarke  was 38 not out as Australia reached its target of
133 in 28 overs.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  